, \"\"]}','2026-07-09 01:23:10','2026-07-12 11:41:29'),('aria','爱芮','异常','以太','[]','/character/aria.webp','队伍中任意角色对敌人施加[侵蚀]效果时，该效果的持续时间提升3秒。','{\"hp\": 7749, \"atk\": 863, \"def\": 619, \"pen\": 0, \"critDmg\": 50, \"mastery\": 116, \"penRate\": 0, \"critRate\": 5, \"dmgBonus\": 0, \"anomalyMult\": 62.5, \"directDmgMult\": 100, \"anomalyCritDmg\": 0, \"anomalyCritRate\": 0, \"anomalyDmgBonus\": 0, \"anomalyDuration\": 10, \"disorderBaseMult\": 450, \"disorderCompMult\": 62.5, \"disorderDmgBonus\": 0, \"turbulenceBaseMult\": 650, \"turbulenceCompMult\": 62.5, \"turbulenceDmgBonus\": 0}','[\"若未与南宫羽、爱芮组队，请自行为全队添加50点攻击力。\\n\\n队伍中任意角色对敌人施加[侵蚀]效果时，该效果的持续时间提升3秒。\\n（！！！注意：乱流补偿倍率吃不到这3秒加成，需减掉！！！）\", \"爱芮触发[异放]时有概率触发暴击：基础暴击率为25%，暴击伤害为25%；若初始异常掌控大于100点，每超过1点初始异常掌控会使该效果的暴击率额外提升0.5%。\\n（对[异放]生效，故既不参与异常伤害，也不参与紊乱伤害！）\", \"爱芮攻击和触发[异放]时无视目标16%防御力；在[妄想时刻]持续时间内，攻击和触发[异放]时额外无视目标8%防御力。\\n\\n注意：减防仅对[异放]生效，对异常伤害无效，因为减防的数值不参与异常条质量计算，而是异常出伤时进行实时计算的。\", \"\", \"\", \"\", \"爱芮进入[妄想时刻]后将不会退出，强化版[普通攻击：绝对音准]和[终结技]造成的以太伤害提升40%，其打出的积蓄同样有40%增伤。\"]','[{\"selfMods\": {\"atk\": 0, \"pierce\": 0, \"resPen\": 0, \"critDmg\": 0, \"mastery\": 90, \"penRate\": 0, \"special\": 0, \"critRate\": 0, \"dmgBonus\": 0, \"vulnerable\": 0, \"anomalyMult\": 0, \"directDmgMult\": 0, \"reduceDefense\": 0, \"anomalyCritDmg\": 0, \"anomalyCritRate\": 0, \"anomalyDmgBonus\": 0, \"anomalyDuration\": 3, \"disorderBaseMult\": 0, \"disorderCompMult\": 0, \"disorderDmgBonus\": 0, \"externalHpPercent\": 0, \"inCombatHpPercent\": 0, \"staggerVulnerable\": 0, \"externalAtkPercent\": 0, \"inCombatAtkPercent\": 0, \"turbulenceBaseMult\": 0, \"turbulenceCompMult\": 0, \"turbulenceDmgBonus\": 0}, \"teamMods\": {\"atk\": 0, \"pierce\": 0, \"resPen\": 0, \"critDmg\": 0, \"mastery\": 0, \"penRate\": 0, \"special\": 0, \"critRate\": 0, \"dmgBonus\": 0, \"vulnerable\": 0, \"anomalyMult\": 0, \"directDmgMult\": 0, \"reduceDefense\": 0, \"anomalyCritDmg\": 0, \"anomalyCritRate\": 0, \"anomalyDmgBonus\": 0, \"anomalyDuration\": 3, \"disorder